name: Millionaires don't use Numerology, but Billionaires do.
description:
Do you ever watch a speech, and it just feels as though there is something being said that is just under the surface? I remember when Madame Christine Lagarde, the then Managing Director of the International Monetary Fund, gave a speech at the National Press Club Luncheon in 2014. Madame Lagarde started explaining how everyone knew how to 'compress numbers' as per Numerology. I was amazed. Here, the center of logical, financial, and mathematical thinking, and the presentation started with a deep dive into the "magic number 7" and how it related to many financial and historical events from 2014. How many of the 'world crafters' in power use such phenomena in their practices and decisions? What was meant about 7 strong years after 2014? Only time will tell. 
At least we know that this event will always be held on the blockchain, #ForTheRecordNFT. 

Original music by @QPrawNFT. 

(all direct quotes from the speech are for journalistic purposes)
